quran[9{c,v,t}:
10,89,khuda ne farmaya ke tumhari dua qubool karli gayi to tum saabit qadam rehna aur be aqlon ke raste nah chalna
10,90,aur hum ne bani Israel ko darya se paar kardiya to firaon aur is ke lashkar ne sar kashi aur ta-adi se un ka taqubkiya. yahan taq ke jab is ko ghark ( ke azaab ) ne aapkrha to kehnay laga ke mein imaan laya ke jis ( khuda ) par bani Israel imaan laaye hain is ke siwa koi mabood nahi aur mein farmabardaron mein hon
10,91,( jawab mila ke ) ab ( imaan lata hai ) halaank to pehlay nafarmani karta raha aur mufsid bana raha
10,92,to aaj hum tairay badan ko ( darya se ) nikaal len ge taakay to pichlon ke liye Ibrat ho. aur bohat se log hamari nishanion se be khabar hain
10,93,aur hum ne bani Israel ko rehne ko umdah jagah di aur khanay ko pakeeza cheezein ataa kee lekin woh bawajood ilm honay ke ikhtilaaf karte rahay. be shak jin baton mein woh ikhtilaaf karte rahay hain tumhara perwar-digaar qayamat ke din un mein un baton ka faisla kardey ga
10,94,agar tum ko is ( kitaab ke ) baray mein jo hum ne tum par nazil ki hai kuch shak ho to jo log tum se pehlay ki ( utreen hui ) kitaaben parhte hain un se pooch lau. tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se tumahray paas haq aachuka hai to tum hargiz shak karne walon mein nah hona
10,95,aur nah un logon mein hona jo khuda ki ayaton ki takzieeb karte hain nahi to nuqsaan uthao ge
10,96,jin logon ke baray mein khuda ka hukum ( azaab ) qarar pachka hai woh imaan nahi laane ke
10,97,jab taq ke azaab alim nah dekh len khuwa un ke paas har ( terhan ki ) nishani aajay
